<p><a title="The Dumps" href="http://www.honeyhelpyourself.com/2010/03/14/the-dumps/" target="_blank">The Dumps</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/honeyhelpyourself/~4/QKwFFJbGI8I" height="1" width="1"/>]]></content:encoded>
